{"type": "article", "id": 14291, "title": "石像花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-02T07:21:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000329U18OWiZvcoGla34j.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这两个花瓶来自意大利的设计师 Raul Frollà，灵感来源于复活岛上的石像，两侧的把手模拟了人像的两只耳朵，的确有单纯静穆的力量。瓶身没有任何装饰，采用浅灰或天蓝两种纯色，非常光洁干净，以反衬出花朵的鲜艳。这组花瓶有高矮两种型号，分别售价 104.3 美元和 98.69 美元。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/moai-terracotta-vase/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141915RhaCuZdBnDg31j87.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"850\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.90425532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141915YIUq7y1smAO9JnDS.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"457\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48617021\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141916maFkXQn3HDcr4Lv8.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}